General.Name: UTA Acquisition Corp Unit
General.Description: UTA Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. The company intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus its search for a target business operating in the gaming, digital media, creator economy, entertainment, and technology industries. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
